When a backtest finishes, write:

    backtest_metric (Sharpe, MaxDD, WinRate,…)

    backtest_equity_curve (ts,equity,drawdown)

    backtest_trade, backtest_order, backtest_signal

    A small job to update strategy_performance rollup from the newest successful backtest_run.

For paper trading, append paper_equity_curve every bar/heartbeat, maintain paper_position, and create paper_trade on each close.

Models: store experiment parameters in model_run.params_json, metrics in model_metric, predictions in model_prediction. Keep serialized model in artifact.